  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Animals</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>There’s a place I’d rather be </l>
          <l>A farm under the sea </l>
          <l>Love to love the animals </l>
          <l>Come and see them playing </l>
          <l>And all the children were so happy, they were playing </l>
          <l>Love to love the animals </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>There is a cow </l>
          <l>There is a chicken </l>
          <l>There is tiger </l>
          <l>He’s in the kitchen </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza"/>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>There’s a place I’d rather be </l>
          <l>A farm under the sea </l>
          <l>Love to love the animals </l>
          <l>Come and see them dancing </l>
          <l>And all the children were so happy, they were dancing </l>
          <l>Love to love the animals </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>There is a fox </l>
          <l>There is a dolphin </l>
          <l>There’s another dolphin </l>
          <l>He’s in the water </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>But the bad neighbors called the police: </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="7" type="stanza">
          <l>“There are too many animals in my yard </l>
          <l>……I can't take it </l>
          <l>Who put the animals here? Fool? </l>
          <l>Take animal away “ </l>
          <l>‘ </l>
          <l>There’s a place I rather be </l>
          <l>A farm under the sea </l>
          <l>Love to love the animals </l>
          <l>Come and see them dead now </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="8" type="stanza">
          <l>And all the people in the village were so sad </l>
          <l>Because they loved the animals</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
